512
00:38:11,670 --> 00:38:13,230
Bahuku.

513
00:38:13,350 --> 00:38:15,550
Apa ini? Berlian?

514
00:38:15,830 --> 00:38:17,590
Berlian?

515
00:38:18,310 --> 00:38:19,950
Apa dia melamarmu?

516
00:38:20,510 --> 00:38:23,190
